<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>A Zend_Mail_Protocol_Exception is thrown in class Smtp::__destruct() if you can't disconnect properly, but throwing an exception from a destructor causes a fatal error with the following message : "Fatal error: Exception thrown without a stack frame in Unknown on line 0"</p>

<p>Code throwing this error :
abstract class Zend_Mail_Protocol_Abstract {
[...]
   public function __destruct()   {
       $this-&gt;_disconnect();
   }
[...]
}</p>

